 this inferred disc\ntruncation is probably not significant given the model uncertainties, it is\nconsistent with the low frequency QPO and gives continuity of properties with\nthe low/hard state spectra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2005 15:11:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Jun 2006 11:10:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-29"}
